headline: Inseego and AT&T Deliver Fixed Wireless Access for Businesses with the Inseego Wavemaker FX4200
summary: Key Takeaways: Inseego and AT&T Business join forces to deliver a powerful, business-grade fixed wireless connectivity solution that’s easy to deploy for businesses of all sizes.Inseego’s Wavemaker FX4200 device helps bridge the gap between overly complex business wireline solutions and simplistic FWA solutions.
